channel.title: Just need a last bit of help!
channel.description:
I'm really sorry for bugging the Hell out of you guys but I need one last thing. I have my routers IP. I've Already Portforwarded. And I have my IP in the setting.ini.
But I need to know [b]EXACTLY[/b] What to do with my routers IP now. Please post every possible step.
I think I got it... I change the server.class file in notepad and where it says localhost i write my internal.
